3. cs.SP (Signal Processing): Sequential compressive sensing is a signal processing technique, and the proposed algorithm is designed to improve its performance. 
4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper includes numerical simulations to demonstrate the performance of the proposed algorithm, which is a common practice in numerical analysis.
